{"tid":531793,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"荷官持刀劫永利4,700萬","createTime":"2018-01-17T07:55:29.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-18T05:09:36.000Z","uid":20933,"like":92,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":89,"replies":[{"pid":"4d31bca29dfd7bd4e8b3f0510852bb1096fd478a","tid":531793,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180117/large/1516171366_852e.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180117%2Flarge%2F1516171366_852e.jpg&h=91beebbf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n澳門發生近年罕見的賭場巨劫案。消息稱，昨晨約8時，一名49歲姓李的荷官，在澳門永利賭場的貴賓廳內突然亮刀指嚇他人，然後劫去大量巨額籌碼(部分面額達100萬)，然後放進預先暗藏身上的環保袋，估計總額達4,700萬。他得手後脫去賭場制服，換上事先準備好的外套，然後由正門逃去。<br />\n<br />\n據悉，該名荷官早有預謀，事先把利刀暗藏於鞋底，以避過賭場保安檢查，現時行蹤不明，澳門司警已發圖通緝。<br />\n<br />\n永利回應稱，案件正由警方處理中"},{"pid":"e4b0de93d703aca48f4cc066b0ea4b45434d2075","tid":531793,"uid":86097,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"ea98adec8cc7f289febb1461c89c8c8916de2c64","tid":531793,"uid":13724,"like":118,"dislike":0,"score":118,"quote":{"pid":"e4b0de93d703aca48f4cc066b0ea4b45434d2075","tid":531793,"uid":86097,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:58:56.000Z","msg":"喺嗰到做無理由唔知，呢單嘢分分鐘有鬼"},{"pid":"c724bf2d197f65c4a4fb07adecc264126515412d","tid":531793,"uid":103207,"like":58,"dislike":2,"score":56,"quote":{"pid":"e4b0de93d703aca48f4cc066b0ea4b45434d2075","tid":531793,"uid":86097,"like":190,"dislike":0,"score":190,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:57:19.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-17T07:59:52.000Z","msg":"拎去買大細,得唔得<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1ca240fcdf378953d327feeb9acbcfb89dd51078","tid":531793,"uid":19126,"like":65,"dislike":3,"score":62,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-